  "text": "There are also other interference models, e.g., Transmitter Interference Model [CITATION_1] and Physical Interference Model. However, in this paper, we mainly focus on joint routing and link scheduling for fPrIM and RTS/CTS models. Note that these two models are different, e.g., in Fig. 1a , links BA and CD can be assigned the same channel in fPrIM model, but not in RTS/CTS model. Similar statement holds for links AB and DC in Fig. 1b .",
